  <refsect1><title>Description</title>
    <para>
      The <sgmltag class="element">academics</sgmltag> element contains
      information about a person's academic experience.
    </para>

    <refsect2><title>Parents</title>
      <para>
        <sgmltag class="element">academics</sgmltag> may be contained in these
        elements:
        <$PARENTS$>
